# Comprehensive WhatsApp Automations & Meta Configuration Plan

We will update the backend logic to handle the complete lifecycle of an appointment with automated messaging via the Meta API.

## Meta Dashboard Setup (Copy & Paste Guide)

You will need to create the following templates in your **Meta WhatsApp Manager** (under Account Tools > Message Templates).
For each template, select **Category: Utility** and **Language: English (US)**.

### 1. Booking Confirmation (`booking_confirmation`)
When booking is assigned or confirmed.
- **Header**: Text -> `Booking Confirmed!`
- **Body**:
  ```text
  Hello {{1}}, your booking at Saachi Shingrani Clinic is confirmed on {{2}} at {{3}}.
  There is a 25-minute grace period if you happen to run late.
  We look forward to seeing you and getting your {{4}} treatment done!
  - Saachi Shingrani Clinic
  ```
- No buttons required.
- *Variables: 1=Name, 2=Date, 3=Time, 4=Service Type*

### 2. Standard Reminder (`appointment_reminder`)
Sent 2 hours before the appointment.
- **Header**: Text -> `Upcoming Appointment`
- **Body**:
  ```text
  Hi {{1}}, this is a friendly reminder for your {{2}} appointment today at {{3}}. 
  Please arrive on time. Reply STOP to opt-out of reminders.
  ```
- *Variables: 1=Name, 2=Service Type, 3=Time*

### 3. Follow-up Reminder (`follow_up_reminder`)
Sent 3 hours before a *follow-up* appointment.
- **Header**: Text -> `Follow-up Reminder`
- **Body**:
  ```text
  Hi {{1}}, this is a reminder for your upcoming follow-up visit for {{2}} today at {{3}}.
  Reply STOP to opt-out.
  ```
- *Variables: 1=Name, 2=Service Type, 3=Time*

### 4. Thank You (No Review) (`thank_you_simple`)
Sent when marked 'Completed' with no review requested.
- **Body**:
  ```text
  Hi {{1}}! Thank you for visiting Saachi Shingrani Clinic today for your {{2}}. It was a pleasure serving you! See you next time.
  ```
- *Variables: 1=Name, 2=Service Type*

### 5. Review Request (`review_request`)
Sent when marked 'Completed' AND review requested.
- **Body**:
  ```text
  Hi {{1}}! Thank you for visiting Saachi Shingrani Clinic today for your {{2}}. 
  We'd love to hear about your experience. Please leave us a quick review below!
  ```
- **Buttons (CTA)**: Web URL -> Type: Dynamic -> URL: `https://your-domain.com/{{1}}` (We will use the tracking proxy path here).
- *Variables: Body 1=Name, Body 2=Service Type. Button URL = leave empty on meta, auto-filled by our proxy.*

### 6. Review Follow Up (`review_follow_up`)
Sent 24hrs later if they didn't click the review link.
- **Body**:
  ```text
  Hi {{1}}, we hope you are doing well after your {{2}} treatment! 
  If you have a spare minute, we'd greatly appreciate your feedback.
  ```
- **Buttons (CTA)**: Web URL -> Type: Dynamic -> URL: `https://your-domain.com/{{1}}`
- *Variables: Body 1=Name, Body 2=Service Type.*

### 7. Cancellation (`appointment_cancelled`)
- **Body**:
  ```text
  Hi {{1}}, your appointment for {{2}} at Saachi Shingrani Clinic has been cancelled. Please contact us to reschedule.
  ```
- *Variables: 1=Name, 2=Service Type*

### 8. Rescheduled (`appointment_rescheduled`)
- **Body**:
  ```text
  Hi {{1}}, your appointment has been rescheduled to {{2}} at {{3}} for your {{4}}. Let us know if this doesn't work for you.
  ```
- *Variables: 1=Name, 2=Date, 3=Time, 4=Service Type*

